01:25:31,300 --> 01:25:33,000
I was a solo singer without a band.

932
01:25:33,500 --> 01:25:37,000
Since I didn’t have members, I became dependent on the machine.

933
01:25:37,500 --> 01:25:47,000
When I sing and play the guitar, the computer aids, that was the way I envisioned.

934
01:25:47,500 --> 01:25:51,000
We proceeded in that way and eventually reached here.

935
01:25:51,500 --> 01:25:54,000
We already used that method a lot when we worked on the first album.

936
01:25:54,500 --> 01:25:58,000
We sampled the phrases of the guitar.

937
01:25:58,500 --> 01:26:03,000
Pressing each keyboard key causes a recorded guitar phrase to sound.

938
01:26:03,500 --> 01:26:08,000
We made songs by playing this keyboard.

939
01:26:08,300 --> 01:26:10,000
We’ve been experimenting with such a variety of things.

940
01:26:10,500 --> 01:26:13,300
It’ll not change much.

941
01:26:13,700 --> 01:26:21,000
Rock music will continue to be played through human groups and machine groups.

942
01:26:22,000 --> 01:26:32,000
According to the genre classification in Japan, it’s called “Visual Rock”, but visual rock doesn’t mean music.

943
01:26:32,300 --> 01:26:38,000
So I wanted to declare it a “Psyborg Rock”.

944
01:26:38,300 --> 01:26:40,000
It’s still questionable if this is a music genre.

945
01:26:40,300 --> 01:26:46,000
I’m making noise that it will be fun if this becomes trend.

946
01:26:49,500 --> 01:26:55,500
Hide has an international mindset that is not limited to Japan.

947
01:26:56,000 --> 01:27:01,000
He is working in Japan because he is a Japanese.

948
01:27:01,500 --> 01:27:07,500
But I think he will be successful enough if he release albums here.

949
01:27:08,000 --> 01:27:14,500
I let my colleagues listen to his music, they were all surprised a lot.

950
01:27:16,000 --> 01:27:22,400
Overall, it’s not much different from the previous two albums.

951
01:27:22,800 --> 01:27:30,000
I think I achieved some of the goals I wanted to achieve in this album.

952
01:27:30,500 --> 01:27:39,500
I think this album will strongly show the fusion of my aspiration as a singer and the rock music I wanted to do.

953
01:28:36,000 --> 01:28:39,000
The future spread in front of him

954
01:28:41,500 --> 01:28:46,000
One night, only me and Hide drank without other people for the first time.

955
01:28:48,000 --> 01:28:49,500
Growth of younger brother.

956
01:28:51,500 --> 01:28:58,000
It was the time to achieve recognition as the aide to Hide and to share the plan for the future.

957
01:28:58,500 --> 01:29:06,400
Hide said “Be my spokesperson so you can speak equally to me”.

958
01:29:06,700 --> 01:29:08,500
I was surprised when I heard that.

959
01:29:10,000 --> 01:29:12,500
Hide would have kept it in his mind.

960
01:29:13,000 --> 01:29:20,000
I speculate that he had a harsh whip on Hiroshi because he wanted his brother to be his spokesperson someday.

961
01:29:20,300 --> 01:29:28,500
Zilch had been trying to do overseas activities since then, hide with Spread Beaver had also been on the rise.

962
01:29:29,000 --> 01:29:38,000
“We are going to be very busy because I am aiming for overseas activities”.

