01:29:38,500 --> 01:29:46,500
He said that he couldn’t fight unless he had the carefully selected staff.

964
01:29:47,000 --> 01:29:53,000
Until then, Hide was the president and the artist.

965
01:29:53,300 --> 01:30:02,000
But from then on he decided to quit the president job and concentrate on the artist job, namely hide’s works.

966
01:30:02,500 --> 01:30:11,500
He didn’t ask me to be the president, but said “Stand in front of people as my spokesperson”.

967
01:30:13,500 --> 01:30:18,000
Artist and manager, older brother and younger brother.

968
01:30:20,000 --> 01:30:22,500
The person he can show his bare face.

969
01:30:26,000 --> 01:30:30,000
“Be my spokesperson”

970
01:30:30,500 --> 01:30:34,000
Hide almost reached the future he always had dreamed of.

