01:31:47,000 --> 01:31:54,000
The “Pink Spider” means a spider that caresses the delusion.

975
01:31:54,500 --> 01:31:59,000
Web spinned by spiders is “web” in English.

976
01:31:59,500 --> 01:32:06,000
Web is the best way for us to gain information.

977
01:32:06,500 --> 01:32:09,500
The internet is an example.

978
01:32:10,000 --> 01:32:18,000
That’s how the spider that spewed the web to collect information should live only in the web that he created.

979
01:32:18,300 --> 01:32:26,000
The spider who doesn’t know other world is deluding himself that the web he spinned is the source of information.

980
01:32:26,500 --> 01:32:30,400
It is a story of a man who is trapped in a delusion and doesn’t know outside.

981
01:32:30,700 --> 01:32:33,700
At last, the spider longs for clouds and flies to another world called sky.

982
01:32:34,000 --> 01:32:38,000
He admires the clouds and ascends to the sky.

983
