01:35:03,500 --> 01:35:09,000
"You don’t know the painfulness of eternal flying as of now."

1007
01:35:10,500 --> 01:35:18,000
"But someday, you’ll realize that you’ve been flying only in someone’s hands, and you have called it freedom".

1008
01:35:20,000 --> 01:35:28,000
Can’t fly well with the borrowed wings, falling headlong.

1009
01:35:31,000 --> 01:35:32,500
“It’s over now”

1010
01:35:36,000 --> 01:35:38,500
“Even though I can see the sky”

1011
01:35:41,000 --> 01:35:43,000
“It is a failure”

1012
01:35:46,000 --> 01:35:48,000
“I wish I had wings...”

1013
01:35:48,500 --> 01:36:14,000
Beyond the barely visible sky, birds are heading south “Let’s fly again, cutting these threads off, with my own jet engine, when that cloud passes by...”

1014
01:36:20,000 --> 01:35:29,500
Pink Spider, the sky is calling me, Pink Spider

