Hide came back from LA where he stayed for a long time for promotion.

1017
01:36:50,000 --> 01:36:55,000
That night, he finished the recording of a TV show and took part in a wrap-up party as always.

1018
01:36:57,500 --> 01:37:02,000
The mood was heightening with his colleagues who have met in a long time.

1019
01:37:02,500 --> 01:37:07,000
That night, he talked about the future of “hide with Spread Beaver”.

1020
01:37:08,500 --> 01:37:16,000
Anecdotes about TV appearance and performance, schedule of tour, things to do as a band, thought about members...

1021
01:37:19,000 --> 01:37:20,000
"I wanna live as a band member."

1022
01:37:22,000 --> 01:37:25,000
"I wanna keep going with my band".

1023
01:37:30,500 --> 01:37:33,500
I thought someone tried to fool me.

1024
01:37:34,000 --> 01:37:39,000
So I decided to come back to Japan.

1025
01:37:39,500 --> 01:37:40,500
I couldn’t believe it.

1026
01:37:41,000 --> 01:37:44,000
I thought there might be a conspiracy.

1027
01:37:52,500 --> 01:37:55,000
I hoped it would be a conspiracy.

