I told him “We can’t see anymore. This is the last time”.

1035
01:39:07,200 --> 01:39:18,000
I came out of the funeral hall holding a portrait of him, and the voice of people from everywhere sounded like scream.

1036
01:39:18,500 --> 01:39:31,000
Compared to their screaming and crying, I thought the portrait was too light.

1037
01:40:10,500 --> 01:40:15,700
[♪Flame] Dear my sun, should I know how low & low?

1038
01:40:16,000 --> 01:40:20,800
Dear my moon, should I know how low & low?

1039
01:40:21,000 --> 01:40:26,000
Dear my stars, if you hear the stars’ lamentation.

1040
01:40:26,200 --> 01:40:31,000
Like a wind, it’s a small sound.

