01:40:31,800 --> 01:40:40,500
Sadness will spread his arms and hug your shoulders.

1042
01:40:42,000 --> 01:40:51,500
He will wrap you with the gently shaking dance.

1043
01:40:57,000 --> 01:40:59,000
It’s the flame of sadness.

