01:41:30,000 --> 01:41:35,000
Even though there wasn’t hide, the third album was completed.

1048
01:41:37,500 --> 01:41:42,000
The person who succeeded Hide was Hide’s right-hand man, I.N.A.

1049
01:41:47,000 --> 01:41:58,000
I wanted to complete the album because I saw the people who gathered in Tsukiji.

1050
01:42:11,000 --> 01:42:13,000
Excuse me.

1051
01:42:18,000 --> 01:42:22,000
Suddenly I recall the memory.

1052
01:42:29,000 --> 01:42:30,500
Sorry.

1053
01:42:34,000 --> 01:42:46,000
I wanted to deliver hide’s songs to the people somehow.

1054
01:42:49,000 --> 01:42:52,000
I will never forget the scene forever.

1055
01:43:03,000 --> 01:43:15,800
I was about to complete the album “Ja, Zoo” on my responsibility.

1056
01:43:16,100 --> 01:43:23,000
I can’t make music, so I asked I.N.A to complete the album in order to deliver it to people.

1057
01:43:23,500 --> 01:43:48,000
I wanted to help people who have cut themselves off from the world and those who have been unable to hear Hide’s music since his death.

1058
01:43:54,000 --> 01:43:56,000
The way to completion of “Ja, Zoo”

1059
01:44:02,000 --> 01:44:05,500
We had to complete the unfinished album.

1060
01:44:05,800 --> 01:44:07,800
Because that’s what hide left.

1061
01:44:08,100 --> 01:44:13,000
There were songs in draft while there were the finished.

1062
01:44:13,500 --> 01:44:17,300
Among them, only the recorded songs could be completed.

1063
01:44:20,100 --> 01:44:27,500
Many people voiced their approval or disapproval on the news that “Ja, Zoo” would be completed without hide.

1064
01:44:30,000 --> 01:44:35,000
It was a very hard work both physically and mentally.

1065
01:44:45,000 --> 01:44:48,000
Until now, hide has been making a decision.

1066
01:44:48,500 --> 01:44:51,500
But from now on, I.N.A is responsible for everything.

1067
01:44:52,500 --> 01:44:57,000
The hardest part was to make a decision.

1068
01:44:58,000 --> 01:45:03,000
Because the person to decide has disappeared.

1069
01:45:03,500 --> 01:45:09,000
The recording began just a week after the funeral.

1070
01:45:09,300 --> 01:45:15,000
I was mentally really messed up.

1071
01:45:23,000 --> 01:45:27,000
I.N.A, use all your talent only for me

1072
01:45:37,600 --> 01:45:44,300
A week before “Ja, Zoo” release, hide’s colleagues started a live tour of 12 locations around the country.

1073
01:45:44,800 --> 01:45:50,000
< October 22, 1998. Yokosuka Arts Theater >
The beginning was Yokosuka, the root and shrine of hide.

1074
01:45:51,000 --> 01:45:59,000
But there were a lot of conflicts between fans, staffs and members about the performance.

1075
01:45:59,500 --> 01:46:03,000
What would hide want to do?

1076
01:46:03,500 --> 01:46:07,000
Wouldn’t he want to play on his tour?

1077
01:46:07,500 --> 01:46:12,500
Someone said, “Let’s make it happen”.

1078
01:46:13,000 --> 01:46:17,300
“Let’s tour. We have to do it”.

1079
01:46:18,000 --> 01:46:20,500
But no one was able to start.

1080
01:46:20,800 --> 01:46:24,000
The members and staffs were people who were with hide when he was alive.

1081
01:46:24,300 --> 01:46:28,500
When we gathered, I felt as if the air sank to the ground.

1082
01:46:29,500 --> 01:46:33,800
Honestly it was extremely painful.

1083
01:46:34,500 --> 01:46:37,500
There is no case that you go on tour without hero.

1084
01:46:38,000 --> 01:46:44,100
We couldn’t expect what would happen.

1085
01:46:44,500 --> 01:46:51,500
We didn’t figure out what to do even though we agonized over it for a long time.

1086
01:46:52,000 --> 01:46:55,000
But we concluded that it’s better to do than not.

1087
01:46:57,000 --> 01:47:00,500
Hide was gone that way.

1088
01:47:01,000 --> 01:47:13,000
But we didn’t think like “It’s over. Dismiss!”

1089
01:47:14,000 --> 01:47:22,000
We concluded that it is better to go on tour both for hide and for the fans.

1090
01:47:22,500 --> 01:47:26,000
Unlike heretofore, hide can’t guide direction anymore.

1091
01:47:26,500 --> 01:47:29,000
Therefore we wondered that who should play hide's role?

1092
01:47:29,900 --> 01:47:31,000
I.N.A had to do it.

1093
01:47:32,500 --> 01:47:37,500
Who would do it if it were not I.N.A? Who else?

1094
01:47:38,000 --> 01:47:44,000
He had been with hide, so we thought it would work well.

1095
01:47:44,500 --> 01:47:52,000
It was “Ja, Zoo” tour without hide, so I had to ask a lot of things to I.N.A.

1096
01:47:52,500 --> 01:47:59,000
But I.N.A said he couldn’t do everything because he was not hide.

1097
01:47:59,500 --> 01:48:04,000
So I worried about what I should do.

1098
01:48:06,000 --> 01:48:10,000
We were so nervous until we started. How should we do?

1099
01:48:11,000 --> 01:48:19,000
JOE said we were the ones that hide chose, so let’s play as a band.

1100
01:48:20,000 --> 01:48:24,000
That was a kind of motive.

1101
01:48:26,000 --> 01:48:28,500
[♪Rocket Dive] High-speeding you are a moment’s spark.

