01:48:57,000 --> 01:49:00,000
The relationship between the members became strange.

1111
01:49:00,300 --> 01:49:03,500
The staff also seemed to be out of their mind.

1112
01:49:04,000 --> 01:49:09,000
On second thought, it was a little reckless.

1113
01:49:09,500 --> 01:49:12,500
But I think it was good to do.

1114
01:49:13,000 --> 01:49:18,000
We started in order to finish it but it does not end.

