01:49:31,000 --> 01:49:44,000
From the beginning of the last live day for “Ja, Zoo”, I kept apologizing for the audience.

1118
01:49:44,500 --> 01:49:57,500
I was grateful to those who came, but I was much more sorry to the audience.

1119
01:50:00,500 --> 01:50:04,000
As the tour went on, the audience enjoyed it.

1120
01:50:04,300 --> 01:50:06,500
Thanks to that, the members were also healed.

1121
01:50:06,800 --> 01:50:11,000
If the tour went on like the first day, members’ hearts would have broken.

1122
01:50:11,500 --> 01:50:23,500
In hindsight, we tried not to distinguish between those who were fans from the old times and the general audience who came to the concert.

1123
01:50:23,500 --> 01:50:30,000
If we split the two, we had to accept hide’s death.

1124
01:50:37,500 --> 01:50:40,000
I was being distressed from start to finish.

1125
01:50:41,500 --> 01:50:50,000
